import React from 'react'
import { Box, Typography, Grid, TextField, Paper, FormGroup } from '@mui/material'



export const Details = () => {
  return (
    <Box >
      <Grid container justifyContent={'center'}>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={6} sx={{ marginTop: 4, boxShadow: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px' }}>
          <Paper
          ml
            sx={{ padding: '10px', height: 'fit-content' }}
          >
            <form>
              <Typography sx={{fontSize:'20px'}}>Create Account</Typography>
              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={3}mb={1}sx={{ fontSize: "16px", color: "#BD4C46" }}>
                    Account Name
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <input
                  type='text'
                  style={{ height: '30px', width: '250px'}}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={3}mb={1}sx={{ fontSize: "16px",  }}>
                    Account Code
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <input
                  type='text'
                  style={{ height: '30px', width: '250px'}}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={3}mb={1}sx={{ fontSize: "16px",color:"#BD4C46"  }}>
                    Account Type
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <input
                
                  type='text'
                  style={{ height: '30px', width: '250px'}}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography
                    mt={2}
                    mb={1}
                    sx={{ fontSize: "16px", color: "#000" }}
                  >
                     Description 
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <textarea
                  rows={3}
                  cols={28}
                  placeholder="Max 500 Characters"
                  style={{
                    padding: "10px",
                    borderRadius: "2px",
                    
                    border: "1px solid gray",
                  }}
                />
              </Box>

             <Box>
             <Typography mt={3}><input type="checkbox" ></input>
               <label  style={{fontFamily:'inherit',marginLeft:'5px'}}>Add to the watchlist on my dashboard</label></Typography>
             
             </Box>

            </form>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

    </Box>
  )
}
